metadata.name: 𝓞𝓻𝓰𝓪𝓼𝓶 𝓲𝓷 𝓜𝓮𝓽𝓪𝓿𝓮𝓻𝓼𝓮
metadata.description:
This painting expresses a new self beyond reality, and shows the new world of Metaverse, which can be proved, and shows the first emotion I felt, "pleasure."
It describes a girl in the shape of an angel to describe her experiences of excitement until she stands at the boundary of death, and a slightly crazy world depicts a feeling of joy that is about to explode.
